Denver Broncos cornerback Aqib Talib and his brother Yaqub are being investigated for aggravated assault after a shot was fired outside a Dallas club . 
  Talib was wanted on charges of aggravated assault with a deadly weapon in 2011 . 
  He and his mother were accused of shooting a gun at his sister's live-in boyfriend in Garland, Texas . 
  He was involved in a physical fight inside Club Luxx on Wednesday . 
  The defensive back was in trouble before and was investigated after an alleged assault on a cab driver . 
 